<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·维清</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson896660f02234">
维清缉熙，文王之典。肇禋，迄用有成，维周之祯。
</div>
</div>
<div class="tool">
<div class="shoucang"><iframe style="width:18px; height:30px; border:0px;" src="/shiwen2017/like.aspx?idsw=265&from=http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=896660f02234"></iframe></div>
